      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "设想你想收到秘密信件，却又不想事先和别人交换钥匙。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39600,
      "text": "RSA 给出了神奇的答案：把锁公开挂出去，钥匙牢牢握在自己手里。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "任何人都能用这把公开的锁把消息锁上，却只有你能打开。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "keygen",
      "line_id": "key-1",
      "filename": "keygen-key-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/xiaoxiao/keygen-key-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "先挑两个素数 p 和 q，把它们相乘得到模数 n。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "keygen",
      "line_id": "key-2",
      "filename": "keygen-key-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/xiaoxiao/keygen-key-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.68,
      "size": 26928,
      "text": "再算出欧拉函数 φ，等于 p 减一乘以 q 减一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "keygen",
      "line_id": "key-3",
      "filename": "keygen-key-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/xiaoxiao/keygen-key-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "选一个与 φ 互质的数 e 做公钥，它的模逆 d 就是私钥。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "encrypt",
      "line_id": "enc-1",
      "filename": "encrypt-enc-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/xiaoxiao/encrypt-enc-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.49,
      "size": 23904,
      "text": "把消息写成一个数字 m，用公钥做加密。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "encrypt",
      "line_id": "enc-2",
      "filename": "encrypt-enc-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/xiaoxiao/encrypt-enc-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "计算 m 的 e 次方再对 n 取余，得到密文 c。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "encrypt",
      "line_id": "enc-3",
      "filename": "encrypt-enc-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/xiaoxiao/encrypt-enc-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "这一步谁都能算，因为公钥 e 和模数 n 是公开的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "decrypt",
      "line_id": "dec-1",
      "filename": "decrypt-dec-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/xiaoxiao/decrypt-dec-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.37,
      "size": 21888,
      "text": "收到密文后，用私钥 d 把它还原。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "decrypt",
      "line_id": "dec-2",
      "filename": "decrypt-dec-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/xiaoxiao/decrypt-dec-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "计算 c 的 d 次方再对 n 取余，奇妙地又回到原来的 m。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "decrypt",
      "line_id": "dec-3",
      "filename": "decrypt-dec-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/xiaoxiao/decrypt-dec-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "想从公钥反推私钥，就得分解出 n 的两个素因子，这极其困难。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "换一对素数，看密钥和模数如何随之改变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "拖动滑块输入不同的数字消息，观察密文和还原结果。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "RSA 用一对素数造出公钥和私钥，公开加密，私密解密。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/rsa-cipher/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "它的安全来自大数分解的困难，守护着今天的互联网。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "rsa-cipher",
      "section_id": "summary",
